      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible, showroom-quality shape\u2014honestly, you'd think it just rolled off the lot! I've babied it since day one, and it shows in every single detail. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
