    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every inch of the deep, metallic finish has been meticulously maintained, boasting a mirror-like shine free of swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and shows zero signs of wear, while the original 'new car' scent still lingers. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively by certified technicians, with a comprehensive folder of records to prove its pampered history. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this is a collector-grade example for the most discerning enthusiast. No excuses, no stories\u2014just perfection.",
      "price": 48750.0,
